**Proposition 4**.: _In setting 2, the spectral gap \(1-\lambda\) of \(CG-MC\) satisfies that for \(\theta>1\),_

\[1-\lambda\geq\frac{1}{2\frac{\ln\theta}{\ln 2p^{*}}\ln 2\theta+1}.\]

