\[\lambda_{2}\leq\frac{2\frac{\ln e}{\ln 2p^{*}}\ln 2e}{2\frac{\ln e}{\ln 2p^{*}} \ln 2e+1}.\]

by plugging \(\tau(e)\) into (7).

