\[P(t+1-\min_{j}t_{m,j}=1) =c,\] \[P(t+1-\min_{j}t_{m,j}=2) =c(1-c),\] \[\dots,\] \[P(t+1-\min_{j}t_{m,j}=n) =c(1-c)^{n-1}\]

